Kasancewar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Turai da Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma United Kingdom, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma Burtaniya, yana tabbatar da cewa duk da cewa yana cikin wani mataki daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da UTIs su kara shirya kansu don barkewar cutar COVID-19 da za su bukaci kulawa da kuma musamman ma magani mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu rahoton wasu cututtukan cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar China ta sanar da mai haifar da cutar a matsayin sabon coronavirus, wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus 2 na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Dalilin da aka samu a yanzu shine cewa kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna da wata nau'i mai sauƙi na cutar, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin su suna warkewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin dari na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya ci gaba zuwa wani mummunan cuta, yana buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na shari'o'in suka ci gaba zuwa wani mummunan cuta, yana buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan marasa lafiya da ke asibiti sakamakon COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin da ake samu na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Birtaniya kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya da na Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasashen EU/EEA da na Burtaniya sun kamu da COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta bazu a wurare daban-daban, kuma motsin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, babban darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na 2020 na Eurosurveillance, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da COVID-19 a Turai, bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon cututtukan guda uku a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da ke dawowa daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an riga an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Burtaniya, kuma a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kwanan wata da aka ambata a sama, an ruwaito shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kawai.
Samun adadi na COVID-19 da kuma adadi na adadi na COVID-19
A Cibiyar Tsare-tsare ta Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka (ECDC), adadin adadin mutanen da aka ruwaito na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushen hukuma kawai, kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, ana sabunta su kowace rana da karfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma a kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin kwatancen yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, mun ƙididdige jimlar kwanaki 14 na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, saboda haka muna la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a tsakanin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin adadin da aka ruwaito daga kowace ƙasa zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8 na safe, kuma mun kwatanta da na Italiya na tsawon 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya
Yanayin da aka samu a cikin kwanaki 14 na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya gaba ɗaya ya biyo bayan na lardin Hubei, China (Figure 1).
A gaba ɗaya, ga EU/EEA da United Kingdom, jimlar cutar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ta ƙaru sosai daga nan zuwa ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya faru ne musamman saboda saurin karuwar shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar yanayin COVID-19 (abubuwan da ke tattare da su).
Hoton 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya ce, a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8 na safe, wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA 15 da kuma Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin da ya yi daidai da na Italiya makonni uku ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka samu a rahoton COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin yawan cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a kowace ƙasa.
Wannan ya faru ne duk da cewa kasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, canje-canje a ayyukan tsarin kiwon lafiya na jama'a na ƙasa, kuma mai yiwuwa, bambancin yanayin ƙayyadaddun lokuta a cikin ƙasashe da kuma yarjejeniyoyi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda za a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwaji don sabuntawa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa a yankunan sun riga sun kai ga iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko a UTI a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA don kawai 6% da 1% na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su a cikin tsari don haɓaka bayanan kulawa na yanzu tare da mayar da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a tsakanin shekara ta 2010 zuwa 2011 ya nuna cewa akwai bambancin da ya faru a yawan gado na ICU da na sashin ICU a Turai, daga gado 29.2 a Jamus zuwa gado 4.2 a Portugal ga kowane mutane 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe za su iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 ICU da kuma magani na rabin-karfi ga yawan mutane 100,000 a tsakanin 2010 zuwa 2011).
An samar da yanayin da aka tsara game da cikawar iyawar tsarin kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya na yawan asibitin COVID-19 da ke hade da haɗarin sama da kashi 90% na ƙarfin gado na ICU, a cikin sabuntawar shida na ECDC's COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment.
Tun da yake har zuwa yanzu akwai wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom da yawa da kuma asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa suna yawanci kula da wani yanki na yawan mutane, ya kamata a ba da bayani game da yanayin kula da gaggawa da kuma gado a cikin Nomenclature na Ƙungiyoyin Ƙasa don Dalilin Lissafi 2 (NUTS-2).
