Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar da cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS), ta kashe mutane sama da dubu 3 kuma ta kamu da fiye da dubu 80 a China da sauran duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga jama'a.
Kamar yadda yake da ƙwayar cutar SARS-CoV, wadda ta haifar da SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar daga bats kuma yana haifar da irin waɗannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 tana da ƙananan tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da yawa fiye da watsawa, kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma maza fiye da mata.
