Ana buƙatar sabunta ka'idodin bincike na "masu zargin" da "masu tabbatar da" COVID-19
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar jagora mai sauri don ganewa da kula da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV). Wannan jagorar tana ba da kwarewarmu kuma yana da kyakkyawan tushe don magance wannan annobar ta duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabon abu ne. Fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ƙwarewa a cikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani akai-akai.
A cikin wannan wasiƙar, mun amsa wani bayani game da jagorarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ƙa'idodin bincike na "abubuwan da ake zargi" da "abubuwan da aka tabbatar" bisa ga sabon Jagorar Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 (sarrafa ta bakwai) da Kwamitin Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya buga.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu ana kiranta cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), kuma an kira cutar coronavirus 2 na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta lasafta COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don magance kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta kirkiro jagorar jagora mai sauri da aka buga a kan layi a cikin Military Medical Research a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Ya jawo hankalin mutane sosai tun lokacin da aka wallafa shi.
Duk da haka, lura cewa COVID-19 sabon cuta ne. Fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da gwaje-gwaje na yau da kullun a cikin aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani akai-akai.
Alal misali, Jagorancin Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 da Kwamitin Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya wallafa tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020 sun yi fitowa guda bakwai tare da canje-canje masu yawa a mahallin wasu.
