Russell Zimmerman, shugaban hukumar masu sayar da kaya ta Australiya, ya ce masu sayar da kayayyaki suna ƙoƙari su ƙara yawan kayayyaki, amma ƙuntatawa na hukumar a cikin yawan aikawa da motoci yana hana hakan.
Yana sa ran samun tsada sosai domin masu samar da kayayyaki suna ƙoƙarin biyan bukatar, kuma ba a ba da tallafi sosai ba.
A ranar Talata, ALDI ta sanar da cewa bayan an saki kayayyakin da wuri, wasu shagunan ba za su iya yin tallata ranar Laraba ba.
A wani rahoto da aka wallafa a News.com.au, Dokta Gary Mortimer, masanin sayar da kayayyaki a Jami'ar Fasaha ta Queensland, ya ce, shaguna suna sake tattara kayayyaki a kowace dare.
Ya nuna cewa takardar bayan gida abu ne mai yawa da ba shi da yawa, kuma idan ya ƙare, yana barin sarari a kan ɗakunan ajiya, yana ƙara jin ƙarancin.
Coles da Woolworths sun yi imani cewa idan akwai yalwa a kan ɗakunan ajiya, idan ana iya sayen kayayyaki kamar takarda mai tsabta da kuma maganin antiseptic kuma suna nan a yalwace, za ka rage tsoro, in ji Russell Zimmerman ga ABC News.
Kamfanin kera takardar bayan gida mai suna Who Gives the Crap ya ce a ranar Laraba ta gabata za su rasa kayayyakin.
Kamfanin Kimberly-Clark, wanda ke samar da takardar gida Kleenex, da Solaris Paper, wanda ke samar da Sorbent, sun jaddada cewa suna aiki awanni 24 a rana 7 a mako don ci gaba da samarwa, a cewar rahoton News.com.au.
Shafin yanar gizon gidajen ƙasa domain.com ya ruwaito cewa wasu masu sayar da gidaje suna ba da takardar wanka kyauta ga masu ba da gwaninta na farko a Melbourne, lokacin da ake yin ƙananan gwanjo tare da masu siye suna shiga hutu a ƙarshen ranar aiki.
Labarin ranar Alhamis na jaridar NT News, jaridar Darwin, ya haɗa da shafi takwas da aka saka don a yanke shi kuma a yi amfani da shi a matsayin takardar wanka.
Da farko, shagunan sun yi jinkirin sanya takunkumi, a cewar wani rahoto na ABC Australia a ranar 3 ga Maris inda suka ce ba su da shirin aiwatar da takunkumi kan sayayya.
Russell Zimmerman ya ƙara da cewa akwai wasu kayayyaki da ake bukatarsu sosai, kamar su masks, maganin kashe cututtuka, kayayyakin bushewa, sabulu na hannu da gari.
Kamar yadda a Ostiraliya, a daren Lahadi, kantin sayar da kayayyaki na kan layi na Ocado na Burtaniya ya ƙuntata sayen takardar bayan gida ta Andres zuwa fakitin 12 na kunshe.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana cutar COVID-19 a matsayin annobar annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana cewa barkewar cutar COVID-19  cutar da coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ta haifar ita ce annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "zazzabin cuta" tana nuna kawai yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda hatsarin da ake samu a wasu lokuta ba, WHO ta nanata bukatar ƙarfafa gwamnatoci su yi aiki:
Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza yanayin annobar.
Idan kasashen duniya za su iya ganowa, gwadawa, bi da su, ware su, su bi su, kuma su tura mutane su yi aiki, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna matukar damuwa da matakan yadawa da kuma nauyi da kuma rashin aiki.
A cewar Dr. Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Amirka, annobar ta "ba a taɓa gani ba".
A cikin wani bayani da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ya ce "ban da mura, ba a lura da wani kwayar cutar numfashi ba tun lokacin da ta taso har zuwa ci gaba da yaduwar duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana mai cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da coronavirus ya fara ba".
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "kuma ba mu taba ganin annobar da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci guda ba".
Sabuwar annobar ta biyo bayan shawarar WHO ta watan Janairu na bayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa na lafiyar jama'a na damuwa ta duniya.
Shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Ƙasar Amirka, Dokta Anthony Fauci, ya ce, cutar "za ta ƙara muni".
A ranar Alhamis, jaridar Associated Press ta ruwaito cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya, inda fiye da mutane 4,600 suka mutu.
Cutar coronavirus ta 201920 annobar cutar ce ta ci gaba da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar ta coronavirus ta cutar ta 2 ta cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disambar 2019, an bayyana ta a matsayin gagarumin matsalar lafiyar jama'a ta duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020 kuma an amince da ita a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu kimanin mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashe 210 da yankuna, inda aka samu kusan mutane 97,000 da suka mutu.
Mutane 364,000 ne suka warke.
An kiyasta cewa yawan mutuwa a kasar Sin ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100, yayin da a duniya ya kai kashi 13.04 cikin 100 a Algeria zuwa kashi 0.08 cikin 100 a New Zealand.
Alamomin da aka fi sani sun haɗa da zazzabi, tari da kuma rashin numfashi.
Abubuwan da za su iya jawo musu matsaloli sun haɗa da ciwon huhu da kuma rashin jin daɗin numfashi.
Lokaci daga bayyanar har zuwa bayyanar cututtuka yana da kimanin kwanaki biyar, amma zai iya kasancewa daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Babu wani maganin rigakafi ko maganin rigakafi da aka sani.
Maganin farko shi ne maganin bayyanar cututtuka da kuma tallafi. Abubuwan da ake ba da shawara na rigakafi sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe bakinka yayin tari, nisantar mutane da kuma saka idanu da keɓe mutane da ake zargin suna da kamuwa da cuta.
Hukumomi a faɗin duniya sun amsa da aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, killacewa, rufewa, kula da haɗari a wurin aiki, da kuma rufe wuraren aiki.
Cutar ta haifar da mummunan katsewar tattalin arzikin duniya, jinkirta ko soke abubuwan wasanni, addini, siyasa da al'adu da kuma rashin wadatar wadata da aka kara ta hanyar cinikin da ke haifar da firgici.
Makarantu da jami'o'i sun rufe a kasa ko kuma a gida a kasashe 193, suna shafar kusan kashi 99.4% na yawan ɗaliban duniya.
Bayanai marasa kyau game da cutar sun bazu a kan layi kuma akwai wasu abubuwan da suka faru na rashin jin daɗin jama'a da nuna bambanci ga Sinawa, mutanen da suka fito daga gabashin Asiya da kudu maso gabashin Asiya da kuma wasu mutane daga yankunan da cutar ta kamu da su.
Saboda rage yawan tafiye-tafiye da kuma rufe masana'antu masu nauyi, an rage yawan gurɓataccen iska da kuma iskar carbon.
Hukumomin lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei) sun ruwaito wani rukuni na cututtukan cutar pneumonia da ba a san dalilinsa ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 kuma an fara bincike a farkon Janairu, 2020.
Yawancin lokuta suna da alaƙa da kasuwar kayan amfanin gona na Huanan kuma saboda haka an yi imanin cewa cutar tana da asalin dabbobi.
An gano cutar da ta haifar da barkewar cutar a matsayin SARS-CoV-2, wanda aka gano kwanan nan kuma yana da alaƙa da kwayar cutar coronavirus na bat, pangolin, da SARS-CoV. Mutumin farko da ke da alamun sanarwa ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019 kuma bai nuna alaƙa da gungun 'yan kasuwa na' ya'yan itace ba.
Daga cikin rukunin farko na shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, an gano cewa kashi biyu bisa uku suna da alaƙa da kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoton da ba a tabbatar ba na South China Morning Post ya nuna cewa wani hali ya nuna 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, wanda zai iya zama na farko. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa, yayin da sabbin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito suka ragu a China amma suka karu a Italiya, Iran da Koriya ta Kudu, adadin sabbin shari'o'in da ke waje da China ya zarce adadin sabbin shari'o'in da ke China a karon farko.
Akwai yiwuwar rashin sanarwa mai yawa, musamman a cikin mutanen da ke da ƙananan alamun.
A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, an samu ƙarancin adadin cututtuka a tsakanin matasa masu shekaru 19 da ƙasa da haka, wato kashi 2.4 cikin 100 na cututtuka a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya a Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60 cikin 100 na mutanen Birtaniya za su bukaci kamuwa da cutar kafin a samu rigakafin da ya dace.
Abubuwan da aka yi magana a kansu sun shafi yawan mutanen da aka gwada su don COVID-19 kuma waɗanda aka tabbatar da gwajin su tabbatacce bisa ga ƙa'idodin hukuma.
Har zuwa 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin 100 na yawanta, kuma wasu ƙasashe sun ɗauki manufofin hukuma na kada a gwada mutane kawai da ƙananan alamun cutar, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka wallafa a ranar 16 ga Maris ya gano cewa a kasar Sin, a ranar 23 ga Janairu, an kiyasta cewa kashi 86 cikin 100 na kamuwa da COVID-19 ba a gano su ba kuma wadannan kamuwa da cutar da ba a rubuta su ba ne suka zama tushen kamuwa da cutar ga kashi 79 cikin 100 na kamuwa da cutar da aka rubuta.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka wallafa a ranar 30 ga Maris ya nuna cewa yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Italiya ya fi yawan wadanda aka ruwaito.
An kiyasta cewa adadin haihuwa na asali (R0) na COVID-19 ya kasance 1.4 zuwa 2.4.
Wani bincike da Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Amirka ta wallafa ya nuna cewa zai iya zama 5.7.
Yawancin mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna warkewa.
Ga waɗanda ba su warke ba, tsawon lokaci daga bayyanar cututtuka zuwa mutuwa ya kai kwanaki 6 zuwa 41, kwanaki 14 ne suka fi kowa.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an yi rahoton mutuwar kusan 97,000 da COVID-19.
A kasar Sin, har zuwa 5 ga Fabrairu, kimanin kashi 80% na mutuwar sun faru ne a cikin mutanen da suka wuce shekaru 60 da haihuwa, kuma kashi 75% suna da yanayin kiwon lafiya na farko, gami da cututtukan zuciya da ciwon sukari.
Yawan mutanen da suka mutu daga COVID-19 na iya zama mafi girma, tun da ba za su iya haɗa da mutanen da suka mutu ba tare da sun yi gwajin ba, misali, waɗanda suka mutu a gida, a gidajen marasa lafiya, da dai sauransu.
Bayanai na Italiya sun nuna cewa adadin mutuwar da aka samu a lokacin annobar ya wuce adadin mutuwar COVID ta hanyar kashi 4-5x.
Wata kakakin cibiyar kula da cututtuka da rigakafin cututtuka ta Amurka (CDC) ta amince cewa "mun san cewa [adadin mutuwar hukuma] an yi kasawa", sanarwa da rahoton rahoton rahoton da aka samu a Amurka. Wannan kasawa yana faruwa a cikin annobar cutar kamar cutar sankarar alade ta H1N1 a shekarar 2009.
Mutuwar farko a wajen kasar Sin ta faru ne a ranar 1 ga watan Fabrairu a Philippines, kuma mutuwar farko a wajen Asiya ta faru ne a Faransa a ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu.
A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, a wajen kasar Sin, an samu mutuwar mutane fiye da goma sha biyu a Iran da Koriya ta Kudu da kuma Italiya.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, fiye da ƙasashe da yankuna arba'in sun ba da rahoton mutuwar a duk nahiyoyi sai dai Antarctica.
Wadannan lambobi sun bambanta bisa ga yankin da kuma tsawon lokaci kuma suna rinjayar yawan gwaje-gwaje, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani, tsawon lokaci tun farkon barkewar cutar da halayen yawan jama'a kamar shekaru, jinsi da lafiyar gaba ɗaya.
Bisa ga kididdigar Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, yawan mutuwar duniya ya kai kashi 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) har zuwa 10 ga Afrilu, 2020.
Yawan ya bambanta bisa ga yankin.
A kasar Sin, ƙididdigar yawan mutuwar ta ragu daga kashi 17.3 cikin dari (a cikin mutanen da suka fara bayyanar cututtuka tsakanin 1-10 ga Janairu na 2020) zuwa kashi 0.7 cikin dari (ga mutanen da suka fara bayyanar cututtuka bayan 1 ga Fabrairu na 2020). Sauran matakan sun haɗa da CFR, wanda ke wakiltar yawan mutanen da aka gano da ke mutuwa saboda cutar, da kuma cutar kamuwa da cuta (IFR), wanda ke wakiltar yawan waɗanda suka kamu da cutar (masu gano da marasa gano) da ke mutuwa saboda cutar.
Waɗannan kididdigar ba su da tsayayye a kan lokaci kuma suna bin wani yawan mutane na musamman na kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar warware matsalar.
Wasu masana sun yi ƙoƙarin yin lissafin waɗannan lambobin don wasu al'ummomi.
Cibiyar Nazarin Kimiyya ta Jami'ar Oxford ta kiyasta cewa yawan kamuwa da cutar ta cutar ta kasance tsakanin kashi 0.1 zuwa 0.39%.
Wannan ƙididdigar ta sama ta wannan zangon ta dace da sakamakon gwajin farko na COVID-19 a Jamus da kuma nazarin kididdiga wanda ya bincika tasirin gwajin akan ƙididdigar CFR.
Hukumar ta WHO ta ce za a iya sarrafa annobar.
Ba a san lokacin da za a yi annobar ba kuma za a iya canja wurin da ya dace.
Maciej Boni, daga Jami'ar Jihar Pennsylvania, ya ce: "Ba tare da a kula da su ba, cututtuka masu kamuwa da cuta sukan kai ga ƙaruwa kuma su koma baya sa'ad da babu masu kula da cutar.
Amma ba zai yiwu a yi wani hasashen da ya dace a yanzu game da lokacin da hakan zai faru ba".
Babban mai ba da shawara kan harkokin likitancin gwamnatin kasar Sin, Zhong Nanshan, ya ce "za a iya kammala shi a watan Yuni" idan dukan ƙasashe suka yi aiki don bin shawarwarin WHO game da matakan hana yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, Adam Kucharski, na Makarantar Lafiya da Lafiya ta Tropical a London, ya bayyana cewa SARS-CoV-2 "mai yiwuwa zai ci gaba da yawo har shekara guda ko biyu".
A cewar wani bincike na Imperial College, wanda Neil Ferguson ya ja-goranci, ana bukatar nisantar jiki da kuma wasu matakai "har sai an samu allurar (mai yiwuwa a cikin watanni 18 ko fiye)".
William Schaffner na Jami'ar Vanderbilt ya ce: "Ina ganin ba zai yiwu ba cewa wannan coronavirus ya ɓace gaba ɗaya, tun da yake yana da matukar yaduwa" kuma "yana iya zama cuta ta yanayi, yana sake bayyana a kowace shekara".
Idan ya sake faruwa, zai dogara ne da rigakafin rukuni da kuma tsawon lokacin da ya faru.
Alamun COVID-19 na iya zama marasa ƙayyadaddun kuma waɗanda suka kamu da cutar na iya zama marasa bayyanar cututtuka.
Abubuwan da suka fi kowa a cikin cututtuka biyu sune zazzabi (88%) da kuma tari (68%).
Alamomin da ba a saba gani ba sun haɗa da gajiya, fitowar numfashi (sneak), rashin jin ƙanshi, rashin numfashi, ciwon tsoka da naƙasa, ciwon wuya, ciwon kai, sanyi, zagi, haemoptysis, diarrhea ko cyanosis. WHO ta ce kusan mutum ɗaya cikin shida yana rashin lafiya sosai kuma yana da wahalar numfashi.
Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka (CDC) na Amurka sun lissafa alamun gaggawa su ne wahalar numfashi, ciwo ko matsa lamba a kirji, rikicewar kwatsam, wahalar tafiya da fuska ko lebe masu launin shuɗi. Ana ba da shawarar neman taimakon likita idan waɗannan alamun sun kasance. Ci gaban cutar na iya haifar da mummunan huhu, cutar rashin jin daɗin numfashi mai tsanani, sepsis, mummunan rauni, da mutuwa.
Wasu daga cikin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar na iya zama marasa alamar bayyanar cututtuka, amma sakamakon gwajin da ya tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar ya nuna cewa sun kamu da cutar, saboda haka masu bincike sun ba da shawarar cewa a saka idanu da kuma duba waɗanda suka yi kusa da wanda ke da kamuwa da cutar don a kawar da kamuwa da cutar.
Ƙididdigar kasar Sin na yawan marasa lafiya sun bambanta daga kashi 44 zuwa kashi 100.
Lokacin da ake amfani da shi na yau da kullum (lokacin da ke tsakanin fara kamuwa da cuta da bayyanar cututtuka) ya bambanta daga kwana ɗaya zuwa 14, amma yawanci kwana biyar ne. A matsayin misali na rashin tabbas, kimantawar adadin mutanen da ke da COVID-19 da suka rasa ƙanshi da farko ya kasance 30% kuma daga baya ya ragu zuwa 15%.
Har yanzu ana gano wasu bayanai game da yadda cutar take yaduwa.
An yi imanin cewa wannan cuta tana yadawa ne ta hanyar tuntuɓar kusa da ƙananan saukad da aka yi yayin yin tari, numfashi ko magana, kuma ana ɗaukar kusanci daga mita 1-2 (3 zuwa 6 feet).
Nazarin ya nuna cewa yin tari ba tare da rufe bakinka ba zai iya sa ka ji kamar ka yi tsatsa daga mita 15 zuwa mita 27.
Wasu mutane sun ce za a iya watsa kwayar cutar ta hanyar saukad da da ke cikin iska na tsawon lokaci, wanda za a iya samarwa yayin tattaunawa. Hakanan za a iya samar da saukad da numfashi yayin numfashi, gami da magana, kodayake cutar ba ta tsayawa a tsaye ba.
Sa'ad da aka yi amfani da maganin, za a iya samun saɓo a bakin da hanci na mutanen da ke kusa da su ko kuma a yi musu iska.
Wasu hanyoyin likita kamar su allura da kuma karyar zuciya da huhu (CPR) na iya haifar da kumburi na numfashi wanda ke haifar da yaduwar iska.
Ƙari ga haka, za a iya samun yaduwar idan mutum ya taɓa wani gurɓataccen wuri, har da fata, sa'an nan kuma ya taɓa idanunsa ko hanci ko bakinsa.
Ko da yake akwai damuwa cewa zai iya yaduwa ta cikin fitsari, an yi imanin cewa haɗarin hakan ba shi da yawa.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta musanta yiwuwar watsa SARS-CoV-2 daga zinare zuwa cikin jini. Kwayar cutar tana da yawa a cikin kwanaki uku na farko bayan bayyanar cututtuka, kodayake watsawa na iya yiwuwa kafin bayyanar cututtuka da kuma a cikin matakan cutar.
An gwada cutar a kwanaki uku kafin bayyanar cututtuka, wanda ya nuna cewa za a iya watsa ta kafin bayyanar cututtuka.
Akwai wasu rahotanni na asymptomatic da aka tabbatar da su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, amma an gano rashin alamar cutar a wasu ƙasashe a lokacin bincike na tuntuɓar.
Cibiyar Tsare-tsaren Cutar ta Turai (ECDC) ta ce ko da yake ba a san yadda cutar take yaduwa ba, mutum ɗaya yakan kamu da mutane biyu zuwa uku.
Musamman, an gano cewa cutar tana iya ganowa har zuwa kwanaki uku a cikin filastik (polypropylene) da karfe 304, kwana ɗaya a cikin kwali da har zuwa sa'o'i huɗu a cikin tagulla.
Amma, wannan ya bambanta bisa ga yanayin zafi da zafin jiki. Dabbobin gida da sauran dabbobi sun riga sun gwada tabbatacce ga COVID-19.
Babu wata hujja da ta nuna cewa dabbobi za su iya canja wurin cutar zuwa mutane, amma hukumomin Birtaniya sun ba da shawarar wanke hannuwanku bayan kun taɓa dabbobi ko kuma bayan kun taɓa wani yanki da mutane suka taɓa.
Coronavirus 2 na cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2) sabon kwayar cuta ne, wanda aka fara ware daga mutane uku da ke fama da cutar huhu da ke da alaƙa da wasu cututtukan cutar numfashi mai tsanani a Wuhan.
Dukkanin halayen sabon SARS-CoV-2 suna kama da na coronavirus da ke da alaƙa da su a cikin yanayin su. A waje da jikin mutum, kwayar cutar tana mutuwa ta sabulu na gida, wanda ke narkar da ɓoye mai kariya. SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da asalin SARS-CoV.
An yi imanin cewa yana da asali na dabbobi.
