An samu mutum na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Wuhan a ranar 1 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019. Wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ya nuna wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar a ranar 17 ga watan Nuwamba.
