Hukumar kula da lafiyar kasar ta ruwaito wani gagarumin karuwa a cikin wadanda aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 20 ga watan Fabrairu, wanda aka danganta shi ne da taron da aka yi a Daegu na wani sabon addini da ake kira Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
An yi zargin cewa masu bauta wa Shincheonji da suka ziyarci Daegu daga Wuhan ne suka haddasa barkewar cutar.
