An kuma shafi jadawalin jiragen sama kuma an canza su. Koriya ta Kudu ta gabatar da abin da aka ɗauka shine mafi girma da kuma mafi kyawun shirin duniya dangane da tantancewa ga cutar. Ƙasar ta kuma ware mutanen da suka kamu da cutar kuma ta gano da kuma killace duk wanda ya tuntube su.
Hanyoyin tantancewa sun haɗa da bayar da rahoton bayyanar cututtuka na mutum ga waɗanda suka dawo daga tafiye-tafiye na duniya ta hanyar aikace-aikacen hannu, gwajin kwayar ta drive-thru, tare da sakamakon da ke samuwa a rana mai zuwa, da kuma ƙara ƙarfin gwaji, wanda ya ba da damar gwada mutane 20,000 a kowace rana.
An yi la'akari da shirin Koriya ta Kudu a matsayin nasara wajen sarrafa barkewar cutar, ko da yake bai sanya birane gaba ɗaya cikin killace ba.
