Iran ta tabbatar da farkon kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Qom, inda, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita, mutane biyu suka mutu a wannan rana.
Matakan da gwamnatin ta sanar sun hada da sokewa na kide kide da sauran al'adu, wasanni, da kuma ayyukan addini a ranar Juma'a, rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi, da makarantu.
Iran ta ba da dala tiriliyan biyar don yaki da cutar.
Shugaban kasar Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairun 2020 cewa ba shi da shirin yin kwarantina a yankunan da cutar ta shafa, kuma za a sanya mutane ne kawai a cikin kwarantina.
An sanar da tsare-tsaren rage tafiye-tafiye tsakanin biranen a watan Maris, ko da yake ana ci gaba da yin manyan zirga-zirga tsakanin biranen kafin Sabuwar Shekara ta Farisa.
Shaidu masu ibada a Qom sun kasance a bude ga mahajjata har zuwa 16 ga Maris 2020. Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China a watan Fabrairu.
A cikin zargin rufewa da yaduwar cutar a Iran, fiye da kasashe goma sun biye da shari'o'in da suka shafi Iran a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu suna nuna cewa yaduwar cutar na iya zama mafi tsanani fiye da shari'o'in 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito zuwa wannan lokacin.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, inda mambobi 23 daga cikin 290 suka tabbatar da cewa sun kamu da cutar a ranar 3 ga Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta yi kira da gaggawa ga hukumomin kurkuku na Iran da su saki 'yancin bil adama da ke fursuna saboda rashin amincewa da zaman lafiya, kuma su sake dukan fursunonin da suka cancanta.
