A ranar 21 ga Maris, an bayyana gaggawa na lafiyar dan Adam a Ostiraliya.
Saboda ingantaccen killacewar jigilar jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da yawa sun shirya janye 'yan ƙasarsu da jami'an diflomasiyya daga yankin, da farko ta hanyar jiragen haya na ƙasar asali, tare da sakin hukumomin China.
Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Ostiraliya, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus da Thailand suna cikin waɗanda suka fara shirin janye 'yan ƙasarsu.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta cire 'yan kasar da suka fito daga kasar Sin ba.
A ranar 7 ga watan Fabrairu, Brazil ta janye 'yan Brazil 34 ko kuma 'yan uwa da suka fi su hudu' yan Poland, da na kasar Sin da na Indiya.
'Yan ƙasar Poland, China da Indiya sun sauka a Poland, inda jirgin ya tsaya kafin ya ci gaba da tafiya zuwa Brazil.
'Yan kasar Brazil da suka tafi Wuhan sun kasance a cikin killace a wani sansanin soja kusa da Brasilia.
A wannan rana, an kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (176 daga jirgin farko, da 39 daga jirgin biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta haya) daga Wuhan kuma an tura su zuwa Tushen Sojan Sama na Trenton don a yi musu killace na makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama da ke dauke da 'yan Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a sansanin sojojin Kanada na Trenton.
Hukumomin Ostiraliya sun kai 'yan kasar 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga Fabrairu zuwa Cibiyar Kula da Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sake amfani da shi a matsayin cibiyar killace su, inda suka zauna har tsawon kwanaki 14.
Jirgin da ke janye 'yan ƙasar New Zealand ya sauka a Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu; fasinjojinsa (gami da wasu daga Australia da Pacific) an killace su a wani sansanin jiragen ruwa a Whangaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta janye Amurkawa daga jirgin ruwa na Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama da ke dauke da fasinjoji 129 na Kanada da aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess, ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara janye 'yan kasar daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga Maris, wani jirgin saman South African Airways da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta haya ya koma da 'yan kasar Afirka ta Kudu 112.
An yi bincike na likita kafin a kai jirgin, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu hudu da suka nuna alamun cutar coronavirus a baya don rage haɗarin.
Sai dai 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka samu gwajin da bai dace ba ne aka mayar da su.
Sakamakon gwajin ya saki dukkan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin agaji waɗanda, a matsayin matakin rigakafi, suka kasance a cikin kallo da keɓewa na kwanaki 14 a Resort The Ranch.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki a wani ɓangare saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen China ta bayyana cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da taimako zuwa kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen aika taimako ga wadanda cutar ta shafa a kasar Sin, tare da wata kungiya a yankin Greater Chicago da aka ce ta samu nasarar aika da masks N95 dubu 50 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa bincike kan alluran rigakafi da kuma kokarin magance su tare da kare "mutanen da ke cikin hatsari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Kamfanin Interaksyon ya ruwaito cewa gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da masks 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya tura masks miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Red Cross ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura tallafin dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da masks miliyan ɗaya ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da fiye da tan 13 na kayan aikin likita zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da kyautar safofin hannu na likita miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayayyakin likita da yawa, gami da tufafi masu kariya 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da tan 17.8 na kayan aikin likita ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin ƙarin dala miliyan 100 a cikin taimakon kuɗi ga ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa. Bayan shari'o'in a China sun daidaita, ƙasar ta ci gaba da aika taimako ga ƙasashe da yawa da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, kasar Sin da Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da kuma kwararrun masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen gudanar da barkewar cutar Coronavirus.
Jack Ma ya tura kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1 da masks miliyan 6 da kuma tufafi 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa a Habasha don turawa ta Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya, ya tura kayan gwaji 5,000, da masks 100,000 da kuma masu iska 5 zuwa Panama.
Ma kuma ya ba da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkiyya, Georgia da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da masks da kuma gwajin gwaji da aka yi a kasar Sin.
Alal misali, Spain ta tattara kayan gwajin Coronavirus 58,000 da kasar Sin ta yi da ƙimar daidaito na kashi 30 cikin ɗari, yayin da Netherlands ta dawo da masks na fuska 600,000 da suka lalace.
Belgium ta tattara masks 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, wanda ake zargin daga kasar Sin ne amma a gaskiya daga Colombia ne.
A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da ayyukan gaggawa na tallafawa kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi na sarrafa cutar da kuma hana ta.
Hukumar ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002 zuwa 2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da yin watsi da bayanai da suka sa hana rigakafi da kokarin dakile ta zama da wuya, da kuma rikicin da ke faruwa a yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ta "bayar da sabuntawa na yau da kullum don kauce wa firgita da ke tafe na bukukuwan sabuwar shekara ta wata".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar manyan hukumomi na aiwatar da haramcin sufuri a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya lura cewa "wannan ba shakka ba shawarar WHO ba ce" kuma kuma "yana da matukar mahimmin alamar ƙaddamar da cutar a yankin da ta fi mayar da hankali". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da watsawa tsakanin mutane daga wajen China da kuma karuwar adadin shari'o'i a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin Bala'in Kiwon Lafiya na Duniya (PHEIC), na shida na PHEIC tun lokacin da aka fara kiran matakin a lokacin annobar cutar sankarar 2009 ta naman alade.
Daraktan WHO, Tedros Adhanom, ya ce an yi kira ga PHEIC saboda "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashen da ke da ƙananan da matsakaitan albashi ba tare da tsarin kiwon lafiya mai ƙarfi ba.
A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa "babu dalilin da zai sa a dauki matakan da ba su da mahimmanci a cikin tafiye-tafiye na duniya da kasuwanci" kuma cewa "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar rage cinikayya da tafiye-tafiye".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa shirye-shiryen dabarun a ƙasashen da ke da ƙananan da matsakaitan kuɗi, ta ambata gaggawa a taimaka wa waɗannan ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin da ke aiki don gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, ko da ta taso".
Tedros ya yi wasu maganganu na baya yana nuna cewa "mu masu karfi ne kamar yadda mu masu rauni ne" kuma ya nemi al'ummar duniya "su zuba jari yanzu ko kuma su biya daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a wani taron manema labarai ya kafa COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya bayyana cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, António Guterres ya amince ya ba da "ikon dukan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a matsayin amsa".
A sakamakon haka, an kunna tawagar gudanar da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ta ba da damar daidaita duk abin da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta amsa, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "daidaita kansu ga amsawar kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya shiga cikin kwarewarsu a fannin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da kuma ci gaban da ke tattare da barkewar cutar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an baiwa WHO ta Joint Mission Team tare da China izinin samar da taimakon masana na duniya da na WHO a ƙasar Sin don gudanar da gida da kuma tantance "zafin cutar da kuma iyawar kamuwa da ita" ta hanyar bitar bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin matakin ƙasa da kuma yin ziyara ta filin don tantance " tasirin ayyukan amsawa a lardin da matakan birni, gami da birane da yankunan karkara". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa "duniya ya kamata ta yi ƙari don shirya don yiwuwar annobar Coronavirus", ta bayyana cewa duk da yake yana da wuri sosai don bayyana annobar, ƙasashe ya kamata su kafa "matakin shiri".
A cikin martani ga barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da Ƙungiyar Gudanar da Ayyukan Hadin gwiwa don kimanta halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce kimantawar barazanar Coronavirus a duniya za ta tashi daga "babba" zuwa "mai girma", wanda shine mafi girman matakin gargadi da kimanta haɗari.
Mike Ryan, darektan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya, ya yi kashedi a wata sanarwa cewa "Wannan sanarwa ce ta gaskiya ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: Ku tashi.
Wannan kwayar cutar na iya zuwa, kuma dole ne ku kasance a shirye", yana mai cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimaka wa duniya ta kauce wa "mafi muni".
Ryan ya kuma ce bayanan da ake samu a yanzu ba su ba da izinin jami'an kiwon lafiya su bayyana cewa annobar ta duniya ce ba, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwa zai nuna cewa "mu a zahiri muna amincewa da cewa kowane ɗan adam a duniya zai kasance a cikin wannan cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana barkewar cutar Coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO tana "da matukar damuwa da matakan da ke damun yaduwar da kuma tsanani, da kuma matakan da ke damun rashin aiki". WHO ta fuskanci sukar da yawa saboda abin da aka gani a matsayin rashin dacewar gudanar da cutar, ciki har da jinkirin bayyana gaggawa na kiwon lafiyar jama'a da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annobar.
Wannan martani ya hada da wata takarda ga Darakta Janar na WHO, Tedros Adhanom, da ya yi murabus, wanda mutane 733,000 suka rattaba hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, da dama daga cikin masana kare hakkin bil adama na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun jaddada girmama hakkin kowane mutum yayin annobar COVID-19.
Ƙungiyar ta ce kowa yana da hakkin ya yi amfani da shi don ya ceci rayuka kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Ƙungiyar ta nanata cewa rashin albarkatu ko shirin kiwon lafiya bai kamata ya zama hujja ga nuna bambanci ga wani rukuni ba.
Masana sun nuna cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da nakasassu, 'yan ƙasa, tsofaffi, marasa lafiya, marasa gida, waɗanda ke rayuwa cikin matsanancin talauci, waɗanda aka tsare, da 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin da ba a bayyana su ba da suke bukatar taimakon gwamnati.
Kungiyoyin gwamnati na duniya suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar al'umma na rikicin COVID-19.
Hukumar Tattalin Arziki da Ci gaban Tattalin Arziki ta kaddamar da dandamali don samar da cikakken bayani game da amsoshin siyasa a ƙasashe a duniya, da ra'ayoyi da shawarwari a kan lokaci.
Daga cikin manufofi don ƙarfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya don magance tasirin ƙuntatawa da ƙuntatawa kan tafiya, cibiyar dijital ta haɗa da Mai Sawun Manufofin Kasar, wanda ke taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da kuma sauƙaƙe daidaitaccen amsawa ta duniya ga ƙalubalen Coronavirus.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta fuskanci sukar Amurka, Ministan ofishin Burtaniya Michael Gove, da kuma dan shugaban Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro saboda gudanar da annobar, wadda ta fara a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kori jami'an jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin a matakin lardin kasar Sin saboda yadda suka bi da kokarin da ake yi na yin rigakafi a kasar Sin ta tsakiya, a wani hali na rashin jin dadin yadda jami'an siyasa suka amsa barkewar cutar a wadannan yankuna.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa wannan matakin na nufin kare babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da barkewar cutar coronavirus.
Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, kamar Zhao Lijian sun yi watsi da ganewar cutar Coronavirus da ta fara a Wuhan, suna goyon bayan ka'idodin makirci game da COVID-19 da suka fito daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Amurka ta Donald Trump ta kira Coronavirus "Cinese Virus" ko "Wuhan Virus" ta ce ƙuntatawa na China "ya wuce gona da iri ga wani cutar da ta zama annobar duniya", wanda wasu masu sukar suka yi la'akari da shi a matsayin wariyar launin fata da kuma "hanyar kawar da gazawar gwamnati don hana cutar".
Jaridar Daily Beast ta samu daga wata hanyar sadarwa ta gwamnatin Amurka da ke da tushe a Majalisar Tsaro ta Kasa, da kuma wata dabara da aka ambata kamar "Dukkanin wannan yana da alaƙa da China.
An shawarce mu da mu yi kokarin samun wadannan sakonni ta kowane hali, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma bayyanawa a talabijin. "Tashoshi kamar Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun nuna cewa kokarin da kasar Sin ke yi na tura tallafi ga kasashen da cutar ta shafa wani bangare ne na tallata tasiri a duniya.
Shugaban harkokin wajen Tarayyar Turai Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai "wani ɓangaren siyasa na ƙasa wanda ya haɗa da gwagwarmayar tasiri ta hanyar ra'ayi mai nuna bambanci da 'yancin kai' siyasa.
Borrell ya kuma ce "Sin tana ba da sako ne da ƙarfi cewa ba kamar Amurka ba, ita ce abokiyar da za a iya dogara da ita".
China ta kuma nemi Amurka ta dakatar da takunkumin da ta dauka kan Syria da Venezuela da Iran, yayin da ake zargin ta tura tallafi ga kasashen nan.
Jack Ma ya ba da kyautar masks 100,000 ga Cuba a ranar 3 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta hana shi yin hakan.
An kuma zargi hukumomin Amirka da tura taimakon da aka ba wasu al'ummai zuwa ƙasarsu.
Kuma ka ji jayayya game da abin rufe fuska da aka ruwaito tsakanin wasu ƙasashe kamar Jamus, Austria da Switzerland; da Jamhuriyar Czech da Italiya.
Bugu da ƙari, Turkiyya ta kama ɗaruruwan masu sanyaya iska da aka yi niyya don Spain.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta soki rashin hadin kai na Tarayyar Turai da waɗanda cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Saƙon Italiya a Tarayyar Turai, Maurizio Massari, ya ce: "Kasin kasar Sin ce kawai ta amsa a bangare biyu.
Hakika, wannan ba kyakkyawan alamar haɗin kai na Turai ba ne".
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan kiran waya da Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya shirya sojojin Rasha don aika da likitocin soja, motocin kashe cututtuka na musamman, da sauran kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Jaridar La Stampa ta Italiya ta yi ƙaulin wani "babban jami'in siyasa" da ba a san shi ba cewa kashi 80 cikin 100 na kayayyakin da Rasha ta kawo "ba su da amfani ko kuma ba su da amfani ga Italiya".
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da kai hari "na siyasa da diplomasiyya".
Shugaban yankin Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, da Ministan Harkokin Wajen Italiya, Luigi Di Maio sun yi watsi da rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai kuma sun nuna godiyarsu.
Rasha ta kuma tura jirgin saman sufuri da ke dauke da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya zuwa Amurka.
Kakakin gwamnatin Kremlin Dmitry Peskov ya ce, "ta wajen ba da taimako ga 'yan'uwansa na Amirka, [Putin] ya ɗauka cewa idan masana'antun Amurka na kayan aikin likita da kayan aikin likita suna cikin yanayi mai kyau, za su yi aiki da juna idan ya cancanta".
Aikin soja na NATO da aka shirya "Defender 2020" a Jamus, Poland da Baltic States, shi ne mafi girma a NATO soja motsa jiki tun karshen Cold War, za a ci gaba da a rage.
Sakatare Janar don Kamfen ɗin Rushewar Nukiliya Kate Hudson ta soki aikin Defender 2020: "A cikin rikicin lafiyar jama'a na yanzu, wannan yana sanya rayuwar ba kawai sojojin Amurka da ƙasashen Turai da dama da ke shiga cikin haɗari ba, har ma da mazaunan ƙasashen da suke aiki". Gwamnatin Iran ta yi fama da cutar, tare da kusan 'yan majalisa goma sha biyu da aka kamu da ita, da kuma manyan siyasa goma sha biyar da ke aiki ko tsoffin' yan siyasa.
Shugaban Iran Hassan Rouhani ya rubuta wasikar jama'a ga shugabannin duniya, yana neman taimako a ranar 14 ga Maris, 2020, yana cewa kasarsa tana fama da fama da cutar saboda rashin samun damar zuwa kasuwannin duniya sakamakon takunkumin Amurka akan Iran.
Masu nazarin siyasa sun yi hasashen cewa hakan zai iya shafar yiwuwar sake zaben Donald Trump a matsayin shugaban kasa a zaben 2020. Dangantakar diflomasiyya tsakanin Japan da Koriya ta Kudu ta tabarbare saboda annobar.
Koriya ta Kudu ta soki kokarin da kasar Japan ta yi na yin kwarantina, bayan da kasar Japan ta sanar da cewa za a sanya kowa da kowa daga Koriya ta Kudu a cikin killace na mako biyu a wuraren da gwamnati ta tsara.
An fara nuna rashin jituwa a al'ummar Koriya ta Kudu game da yadda Shugaba Moon Jae-in ya amsa wannan matsalar.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan bukukuwa suna neman tsige Moon a kan abin da suka kira rashin kula da annobar, ko kuma suna yaba da martani.
Wasu masu sharhi sun nuna damuwa cewa hakan zai iya ba gwamnatoci damar karfafa ikon su.
A Hungary, majalisa ta amince da cewa Firayim Minista Viktor Orbán zai iya mulki ta hanyar doka har abada, dakatar da majalisa da kuma zaben, da kuma hukunta waɗanda ake ganin sun yada labaran karya game da cutar da kuma gwamnatin ta kula da rikicin.
An yi zargin cewa cutar ta Coronavirus ta jawo karancin kayayyaki da yawa, sakamakon karuwar amfani da kayan aiki a duniya don yaki da barkewar cutar, cin kasuwa da tsoro, da kuma katsewa a masana'antu da ayyukan kaya.
Hukumar Abinci da Kula da Abinci ta Amirka ta yi gargadi game da rashin magani da kuma kayan aikin likita saboda yawan amfani da shi da kuma katsewar mai ba da kayayyaki.
Wasu 'yan gida ma sun yi ta cin kasuwa domin tsoro, wanda ya sa kayayyakin da ake bukata kamar abinci, takardar wanka, ruwa mai kwalban, da kuma karancin kayayyaki suka kasance a kan ɗakunan ajiya.
Masana'antun fasaha sun yi gargadi game da jinkirin aikawa da kayayyakin lantarki.
A cewar Daraktan Dinkin Duniya Tedros Adhanom, bukatar kayan kariya ta mutum ta ƙaru sau 100.
Wannan bukatar ta kai ga karin farashin har sau ashirin na farashin al'ada kuma ta haifar da jinkirin samar da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya na watanni hudu zuwa shida.
Hakan ya kuma jawo karancin kayan aikin kare kai a duniya, kuma WHO ta yi gargadin cewa hakan zai sa lafiyar ma'aikata cikin haɗari.
A Ostiraliya, annobar ta ba da sabuwar dama ga masu sayen Sin, daigou, su sayar da kayayyakin Ostiraliya a kasar Sin.
Aikin ya haifar da karancin kayan abinci ga jarirai a wasu manyan kantuna kuma daga baya gwamnatin Ostiraliya ta dakatar da shi. Duk da yawan cututtukan COVID-19 a arewacin Italiya da yankin Wuhan, da kuma sakamakon babban buƙatar abinci, an ceci yankunan biyu daga karancin abinci.
Matakan da kasar Sin da Italiya suka dauka kan ajiya da kuma cinikin kayayyakin da ba a yarda da su ba sun yi nasara wajen kawar da matsalar rashin abinci mai tsanani da aka yi hasashen za ta auku a Turai da kuma Arewacin Amirka.
Arewacin Italiya da yawan aikin gona da ta yi ba ta samu raguwa mai yawa ba, amma farashin zai iya tashi bisa ga masana'antun masana'antu.
An gano shelves na abinci a kan wani lokaci, har ma a birnin Wuhan, kuma jami'an gwamnatin kasar Sin sun saki naman alade don tabbatar da isasshen abinci ga jama'a.
Akwai irin wannan dokar a Italiya, wadda ta bukaci masu samar da abinci su ajiye kayayyaki don irin wannan gaggawa.
An ji lalacewar tattalin arzikin duniya a kasar Sin: a cewar wani rahoto na kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 16 ga Maris, tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ya sha wahala sosai a farkon watanni biyu na shekarar 2020 saboda matakan da gwamnati ta dauka don rage yaduwar cutar, kuma tallace-tallace a kantin sayar da kayayyaki sun ragu da kashi 20.5%.
Tun da kasar Sin tana da babbar tattalin arziki da cibiyar masana'antu, an ga barkewar cutar a matsayin babbar barazana ga tattalin arzikin duniya.
