Nazarin dakin gwaje-gwaje na cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) da kuma cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ta danganta da ita ya haɗa da hanyoyin gano kasancewar cutar da waɗanda ke gano rigakafin da aka samar don amsawa ga kamuwa da cuta.
Ana tabbatar da kasancewar cutar a cikin samfurori ta hanyar RT-PCR, wanda ke gano RNA na coronavirus.
Wannan gwajin na musamman ne kuma an tsara shi ne don gano RNA na SARS-CoV-2 kawai.
Ana amfani da shi don tabbatar da cututtuka na kwanan nan ko na yanzu.
Ana iya amfani da gano rigakafi (sorology) don ganewar asali da kuma lura da al'umma.
Ana gwada mutane da yawa da suka kamu da cutar, har da waɗanda ba su da alamun bayyanar cututtuka sosai don a ba su rahoto ko kuma waɗanda ba su da alamun cutar.
Ana iya sanin ainihin yawan mutuwar cutar da kuma matakin rigakafin garken a cikin jama'a daga sakamakon wannan gwajin.
Saboda ƙarancin gwaji, a watan Maris na shekarar 2020 babu wata ƙasa da ke da tabbacin bayanan cutar a cikin al'ummarta.
A ranar 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin 100 na yawan jama'arta, kuma akwai bambancin gaske a yawan gwaje-gwajen da aka yi a ƙasashe.
Wannan bambancin zai iya shafar yawan mutuwar da aka samu a wasu ƙasashe, wanda za a iya ƙididdigewa sosai.
Ta amfani da real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), ana iya yin gwajin a kan samfurori na numfashi da aka samu ta hanyoyi daban-daban, ciki har da nasopharyngeal rubbing ko saliva samfur.
A yawancin lokaci, sakamakon zai kasance cikin sa'o'i ko kwanaki biyu.
Gwajin RT-PCR da aka yi da farjin farjin yana da tabbaci a mako na farko na rashin lafiya.
Daga baya, cutar za ta iya ɓacewa a cikin garkuwar yayin da take ci gaba da ƙaruwa a cikin huhu.
A matsayin madadin, ga mutanen da suka kamu da cutar da aka gwada a mako na biyu, za a iya cire kayan samfurin daga cikin hanyar numfashi ta hanyar catheter mai tsotsewa ko kuma a yi amfani da kayan fitarwa ta hanyar fitarwa (sakewa).
An yi wani gwajin PCR na farko a Charité, Berlin, a watan Janairun 2020 ta amfani da polymerase chain reaction tare da ainihin lokacin rikodin rikodin (rRT-PCR), kuma yana zama tushen kayan aikin 250,000 don rarraba ta WHO.
Kasar Burtaniya ta kuma ci gaba da gwajin a ranar 23 ga Janairu, 2020. Kamfanin Kogenebiotech na Koriya ta Kudu ya ci gaba da wani nau'i na asibiti, kayan aikin gano SARS-CoV-2 dangane da PCR (PowerCheck Coronavirus) a ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020.
Yana neman kwayar halitta "E" da dukkan beta coronavirus ke rabawa, da kuma kwayar halitta RdRp, ta SARS-CoV-2 ta musamman. A China, BGI Group na ɗaya daga cikin kamfanoni na farko da suka sami amincewa don amfani da gaggawa daga Hukumar Kula da Kayan Aikin Kayan Aiki ta China don kit ɗin gano SARS-CoV-2 na PCR. A Amurka, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafi (CDC) tana rarraba sabon kwamiti na ganewar asali na RT-PCR na Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) a cikin ainihin lokacin ga dakunan gwaje-gwaje na lafiyar jama'a ta hanyar Reagent Resource ta Duniya.
Ɗaya daga cikin gwaje-gwaje guda uku na kwayoyin halitta a cikin tsofaffin sigar kayan gwajin ya haifar da gwaji mara kyau na masu aiki da ƙarancin ƙarfi, da kuma hana gwaji a CDC a Atlanta; wannan ya haifar da matsakaici na samfurori kasa da 100 a kowace rana da aka aiwatar da su cikin nasara a cikin watan Fabrairu na 2020.
Ba a amince da gwaje-gwajen da ke amfani da abubuwa biyu ba har zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma daga nan ne aka ba da izinin fara gwajin ga gida da kuma dakunan gwaje-gwaje na jihar.
Hukumar Abinci da Magunguna ta amince da gwajin a ƙarƙashin izinin gaggawa.
Daga ranar 5 ga Maris, 2020, LabCorp ta sanar da kasancewar gwajin COVID-19 na ƙasa don RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics ta kuma sanya gwajin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasa daga 9 ga Maris, 2020.
Babu wani ƙuntatawa a kan adadi da aka sanar; ana buƙatar tattara da sarrafa samfurori bisa ga bukatun CDC.
A Rasha, cibiyar bincike ta jihar kan cututtukan cututtuka da fasahar halittu, VECTOR ce ta haɓaka da samar da gwajin COVID-19.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Tarayya ta Tarayya ta yi rajistar gwajin. A ranar 12 ga Maris, 2020, Mayo Clinic ta ce ta haɓaka gwajin don gano kamuwa da COVID-19. A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, Roche Diagnostics ta sami amincewar FDA don gwajin da za a iya gudanarwa a cikin awanni 3.5 a cikin sikelin, don haka ba da damar inji ɗaya don aiwatar da kimanin gwaje-gwaje 4,128 a cikin awanni 24.
