A ranar 21 ga Maris, 2020, Cepheid ta kuma samu takardar shaidar Amurka daga FDA don gwajin da zai ɗauki kimanin minti 45.
Hukumar ta amince da gwajin da ke amfani da fasahar isothermic nucleic acid amplification maimakon PCR.
Tun da yake ba ya bukatar a yi sau da yawa a kan yanayin zafi, wannan hanyar tana iya kawo sakamako mai kyau a cikin minti biyar kawai kuma sakamako mara kyau a cikin minti 13.
Akwai kimanin 18,000 na waɗannan injunan a halin yanzu a Amurka kuma Abbott na fatan haɓaka samarwa don samar da gwaje-gwaje 50,000 a kowace rana. Gwaje-gwaje wanda ke amfani da antibody na monoclonal kuma yana ɗaure shi musamman zuwa furotin nucleocapsid (protein N) na sabon coronavirus ana haɓaka a Taiwan, tare da tsammanin samar da sakamako a cikin mintuna 15 zuwa 20 kamar gwajin sauri na mura.
Wani bita na wallafe-wallafen a watan Maris na 2020 ya kammala cewa "rawanin X-ray na ƙirjin suna da ƙarancin ƙimar ganewar asali a farkon matakan, yayin da binciken CT, CT, na iya kasancewa a gaban bayyanar cututtuka".
Abubuwan da ke cikin TC sun haɗa da opacity na biyu-matsakaici a cikin gilashin duhu tare da rarraba baya, na gefe da kuma asymmetric.
Ƙarfi na ƙwayoyin cuta, da kuma ƙirar mosaic da kuma ƙarfafawa suna ci gaba da ci gaba da cutar.
Wani bincike da ya kwatanta PCR da CT a Wuhan a wurin da cutar ta barke a yanzu ya nuna cewa CT ya fi PCR muhimmanci, ko da yake ba shi da ƙayyadaddun bayanai, tare da yawancin abubuwan da ke cikin hotonsa da suka dace da sauran cututtukan huhu da cututtukan cututtuka.
Tun daga Maris 2020, Kwalejin Radiology ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar cewa "Kada a yi amfani da CT don tantancewa ko a matsayin gwajin farko don gano COVID-19". Tun daga Maris 2020, CDC ta ba da shawarar PCR don dubawa na farko.
Wani ɓangare na maganin rigakafi ga kamuwa da cuta shi ne samar da rigakafi ciki har da IgM da IgG.
Ana iya amfani da su don gano kamuwa da cuta a cikin mutane da suka fara kwanaki 7 ko kuma bayan bayyanar cututtuka, don sanin rigakafi, da kuma lura da yawan jama'a. Ana iya yin gwaje-gwaje a cikin cibiyar bincike (CLT) ko ta hanyar gwajin gwaji na nesa (PoCT).
Aikin sarrafa kansa mai ƙwarewa a cikin dakunan gwaje-gwaje da yawa zai iya yin waɗannan gwaje-gwajen, amma kasancewa a wurin zai dogara da yawan aikin da ake yi a kowace hanya.
A cikin CLT, ana amfani da jini guda ɗaya na jini, ko da yake ana iya amfani da samfurori da yawa don lura da amsawar rigakafi.
A cikin PoCT, ana samun jini guda ɗaya ta hanyar bugun jini.
Ba kamar hanyoyin PCR ba, ba a buƙatar matakin tattara kafin gwaji. A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, FDA ta nuna hukumomi 29 da suka sanar da hukumar kamar yadda aka buƙata, kuma daga yanzu sun dace su rarraba gwajin rigakafin su.
Tun daga ranar 7 ga Afrilu, 2020, FDA ta amince da gwaji guda ɗaya kawai tare da izinin amfani da gaggawa. A ƙarshen Maris, 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics da Epitope Diagnostics sun sami amincewar Turai don kayan gwajin su, waɗanda zasu iya gano IgG da IgA antibodies ga cutar a cikin samfurin jini.
