Angiotensin converting enzyme type 2 (ECA2) wani enzyme ne wanda aka haɗa zuwa farfajiya ta waje (ƙwayoyin halitta) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ECA2 yana hana aikin angiotensin mai canzawa (ECA) ta rage adadin angiotensin II da kuma ƙara Ang (1-7), yana zama magani mai alƙawarin da aka yi niyya don magance cututtukan zuciya. ECA2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin halitta don wasu ƙwayoyin coronaviruses.
Ana kiran wannan ƙwayar a matsayin hECA2.
Angiotensin converting enzyme type 2 wani enzyme ne mai dauke da zinc wanda yake a farfajiyar endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Protein ECA2 yana dauke da wani yanki na N-terminal M2 peptidase da kuma wani yanki na C-terminal wanda ke dauke da amino acid da colectin a cikin tsarin koda.
ECA2 wani furotin ne mai ɗauke da membrane mai ɗauke da nau'i na 1 wanda ke da ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta a jikin jikinsa a cikin huhu da kuma sauran kayan jiki.
Ƙarƙashin ECA2 na ƙwayoyin halitta yana ƙetare daga ƙirar transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma an saki furotin mai narkewa a cikin jini kuma an fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ECA2 yana cikin gabobin da yawa: ECA2 yana da alaƙa da ƙwayoyin halitta na manyan ƙwayoyin huhu na jini na II, ƙwayoyin cuta na hanji, ƙwayoyin jini da na jini, da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jini a yawancin gabobin.
Ana kuma samun furcin ECA2 mRNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa, jikin da ke cikin jijiya, da kuma ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa.
Babban aikin ECA2 shine ya zama ma'auni ga ECA.
ECA ta haɗa angiotensin na nau'i na 1 zuwa angiotensin na nau'i na 2, ta sa a yi vasokonstrus.
ECA2 kuma yana haɗa phenylalanine na amino acid carboxiterminal daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) da hydrolysis a cikin vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 kuma yana ɗaure wasu wasu peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradicinine, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ECA2 kuma yana daidaita motsi ta membrane na amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma yana da hannu a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai ƙwayar cuta, ECA2 yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin halitta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na coronavirus, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (virus da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Ƙari ga haka, haɗuwa da ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin ECA2 na enzymatic a saman sel yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma translocation na cutar da enzyme zuwa endosomes a cikin sel.
