Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na hannu don taimakawa sa ido kan cutar coronavirus ta 2019-2020, wato, tsarin gano mutane ("tabbata") waɗanda zasu iya tuntuɓar mutane masu kamuwa da cutar.
