A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnatin ta bayyana cewa aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba yana cikin ci gaba, kuma zai kasance a shirye don rarrabawa a cikin makonni.
Ostiraliya da New Zealand suna shirin aikace-aikace dangane da aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da kuma yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha na shirin aiwatar da aikace-aikacen iyakance ƙasa don marasa lafiya da aka gano suna da COVID-19 suna zaune a Moscow, wanda aka tsara don tabbatar da cewa ba sa barin gida.
Ross Anderson, wani farfesa a jami'ar Cambridge, ya lissafa wasu matsaloli masu amfani da tsarin da ke amfani da aikace-aikacen, ciki har da rashin tabbataccen sakamako da kuma rashin tasiri idan karɓar aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga ƙananan ɓangaren jama'a.
A cikin martani ga damuwar game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" na karya ko cutarwa, Apple ya kafa iyakoki ga nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi waɗanda zasu iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da suka shafi coronavirus zuwa App Store, yana iyakance su ne kawai ga ƙungiyoyi "masu hukuma" ko kuma wasu ƙungiyoyi masu daraja.
Google da Amazon sun yi irin wannan takunkumin.
