Kungiyar Tsaro a MIT Media Lab ta haɓaka Safe Paths, dandamali don amfani da fasahohin kiyaye sirrin yayin tattarawa da amfani da bayanan wuri ko haɗuwa da hanyoyi don bin diddigin yaduwar COVID-19.
Ya dogara ne akan bincike daga littafin fasaha "Apps Play Dirty: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" wanda aka fitar a watan Maris na 2020. Wani irin wannan ƙoƙari shine dandamali na SafeTrace na Enigma MPC, wani kamfani wanda ke haɓaka fasahar tsare sirri kuma an kafa shi a MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace yana amfani da fasahar kayan aiki masu aminci don ba masu amfani damar raba bayanai masu mahimmanci na wuri da kiwon lafiya tare da sauran masu amfani da masu kula ba tare da yin amfani da sirrin wannan bayanan ba.
